---
title: Roasted Pork Tenderloin with Lemony Potatoes & Zucchini
description: If you’ve never had lemony potatoes before, you’re about to be spoiled for all other spuds. They’re equal parts crispy, creamy, tangy, and all around delightful. This starring side is accompanied by tender, roasted zucchini, and the main event, succulent pork tenderloin. It’s all tied together with a rich pan sauce that’s got some zing, thanks to a touch more lemon juice. When life gives you lemons, you know what to do!
